Project structure:

(based on https://github.com/drivendata/cookiecutter-data-science)
(and on https://towardsdatascience.com/structure-and-automated-workflow-for-a-machine-learning-project-2fa30d661c1e)

.
├── data                                
│   ├── external              data from external sources
│   ├── interim               data used in intermediate processes
│   ├── pre                   preprocessed data (processed to allow further processing)
│   ├── process               processed data
│   └── raw                   raw data (ready or not ready to analyse)
│
├── loteca                    source code root
│   └── data                            
│       ├── interim           code here will generate data that goes into './data/interim/'
│       ├── pre
│       ├── process
│       └── raw
├── notebooks                 jupyter notebooks
│   └── html                  html generated from jupyter notebooks (for reading)
└── references                external references (e.g. something about what we are retrieving)
